These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: lemon, plum, onion, orange
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, guinea-pig, rat, bird
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, airplane, train, car
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the person driving the car is the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the person eating onion is on the far left##1
4. the person eating lemon is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person driving the train and the person eating plum##2
6. the person driving the airplane is the owner of the rat##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | onion | orange  | plum | lemon  |
| Pet         | bird    | guinea-pig  | rabbit       | rat     |
| Transport   | train     | subway | car       | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, writing, camping, fishing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, spy, western, crime
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, soccer, volleyball, cycling
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person watching crime movies and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
5. the person watching crime movies is the person who's sport is soccer##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
7. the person watching western movies is the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | writing | rock-climbing    | fishing  | camping |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | comedy  | spy   | western    |
| Sport         | soccer | cycling | weightlifting | volleyball      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, coffee
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, singing, camping, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, disco, rock, soul
1. the fan of disco is between the fan of soul and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the fan of techno##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
6. the fan of techno is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
7. the fan of rock is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | coffee         | soy-milk   | iced-tea    |
| Hobby         | singing | woodworking | hiking | camping |
| Music-Genre   | rock   | disco        | soul      | techno   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, egyptian, italian, japanese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, ice-hockey, handball, parkour
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, jet-ski, trike, subway
1. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the van is between the person driving the subway and the japanese##2
3. the italian is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the italian is on the right of the indian##1
6. the person driving the subway is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person driving the jet-ski##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | japanese        | egyptian   | indian | italian |
| Sport         | handball | skiing | ice-hockey    | parkour |
| Transport     | trike       | van     | subway       | jet-ski    |

