.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, milk, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, baking, camping, dancing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, surfing, rugby, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking iced-tea##2
2. the person who's sport is skiing is the person drinking water##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's hobby is fishing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | cola | water      | iced-tea       | milk   |
| Hobby      | fishing   | baking  | dancing | camping     |
| Sport      | surfing     | skiing | rugby        | skateboarding |

