.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, grapefruit, orange, kiwi
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, hiking, reading, chess
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, biathlon, skiing, tennis
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's sport is skiing##2
6. the person eating grapefruit is between the person eating garlic and the person eating orange##2
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | orange | grapefruit  | garlic | kiwi      |
| Hobby   | reading  | chess  | filmmaking | hiking |
| Sport   | tennis | surfing | biathlon | skiing     |

