.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, banana, pineapple, peach
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, romance, western, musical
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, climbing, biathlon, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person watching scientific movies##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
6. the person eating banana is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching western movies##2
7. the person eating peach is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | pineapple  | banana    | peach | nectarine  |
| Movie-Genre   | western | musical       | romance        | scientific    |
| Sport         | climbing | tennis | skateboarding  | biathlon |

