.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, reading, woodworking, card-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, disaster, time-travel, adventure
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, guinea-pig, goldfish, ferret
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is between the owner of the ferret and the person who's hobby is reading##2
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | card-games  | reading | woodworking | baking |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | adventure | disaster   | time-travel         |
| Pet           | hedgehog | goldfish  | guinea-pig   | ferret      |

