3. the fan of rock is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person eating cucumber##1
5. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating onion##1
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the fan of electronic and the person who's hobby is baking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | onion  | garlic    | blueberry | cucumber       |
| Hobby         | cooking | magic-tricks | baking  | filmmaking |
| Music-Genre   | electronic   | hip-hop      | rock  | pop     |

