3. the owner of the fish is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the owner of the fish and the person eating nectarine##2
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is the owner of the cat##1
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the owner of the horse##1
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the owner of the fish##1

