The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing, puzzles, hiking
4 different pets are kept: fish, guinea-pig, dog, rat
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person drinking water is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking water is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the owner of the fish is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | coffee | soy-milk     | water | hot-chocolate       |
| Hobby      | puzzles  | hiking | collecting  | rock-climbing |
| Pet        | rat  | guinea-pig      | dog        | fish      |

