3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking cola is the owner of the horse##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
