3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the firefighter##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person driving the car##1
5. the person driving the bike is between the person watching adventure movies and the photographer##2
6. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the bike is the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
