The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, punk, electronic, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, british, chinese, brazilian
1. the fan of metal is the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking water is between the person drinking coffee and the british##2
3. the person drinking coffee is the fan of punk##1
4. the person drinking coffee is between the fan of electronic and the brazilian##2
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
6. the pakistani is between the chinese and the fan of trance##2
7. the fan of metal is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
