.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, juice, 7up, hot-chocolate
There 4 different types of food: plum, nectarine, mango, pumpkin
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cycling, snowboarding, water-polo
1. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
2. the person eating mango is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far right##1
5. the person eating plum is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
6. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person eating mango##1
7. the person drinking 7up is the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk    | juice | hot-chocolate           | 7up |
| Food       | plum | mango    | nectarine          | pumpkin   |
| Sport      | snowboarding  | cycling   | water-polo | badminton  |

