The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, superhero, adventure, mystery
4 different pets are kept: pony, dog, rat, guinea-pig
1. the person watching adventure movies is the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person drinking water##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching spy movies##2
5. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person drinking coffee and the owner of the pony##2
7. the person watching mystery movies is the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage      | water | iced-tea | coffee     | almond-milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | mystery        | adventure  | superhero  |
| Pet           | pony      | guinea-pig         | dog | rat |

