The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, lacrosse, skateboarding, parkour
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile, airplane, helicopter
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the lawyer##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is the person driving the boat##1
3. the social-worker is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the airplane is the dressmaker##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is the person driving the airplane##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person driving the airplane##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | social-worker        | dressmaker  | lawyer | architect   |
| Sport       | parkour | rugby | skateboarding    | lacrosse |
| Transport   | boat        | airplane     | helicopter       | snowmobile      |

