.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, lemon, spinach, onion
4 different pets are kept: dog, pony, lizard, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, bike, snowmobile, ship
1. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
2. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
4. the person eating spinach is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the ship is the owner of the snake##1
6. the owner of the pony is between the person eating onion and the person driving the snowmobile##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | onion | lemon | lettuce | spinach |
| Pet         | dog       | pony     | lizard   | snake   |
| Transport   | taxi | bike | snowmobile | ship |

 